				                <div>Hello Brian,<br />
<br />
Thank you for your question. The <a href="http://www.inmotionhosting.com/support/website/htaccess/what-is-the-htaccess-file-and-what-do-i-use-it-for">.htaccess</a> file is specific to Apache Servers, which is what we run.<br />
<br />
