				                <div><p><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;">Hi Scott, thanks for the reply. I was going crazy with this, but I finally fixed it.&nbsp;</span></p>
<div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;">I realized that the problem was from a plugin that generated old pages from my previous permalink set up.&nbsp;</div>
